item.title: First Post
item.description: This is my first post to the blog!
item.content:encoded: This is my first post on my newly-made corner of the internet! I posted an article to Medium in the past, but haven’t gone around to posting anything since. Now that I’ve started my internship, I think this website will be a great place for me to write some short snippets on all the ML and NLP-related stuff I’m learning.
